    • displayManagerProfile

      private void displayManagerProfile(HDBManager manager)
      Displays the profile of a hotel database manager and provides navigation back to the manager menu. This method performs two main actions: 1. Calls the manager's polymorphic displayProfile() method to show the manager's details 2. Waits for user input before returning to the main manager menu
      Parameters:
      manager - The HDBManager whose profile is to be displayed
